  "description": "The fully-integrated Sense.HR optical heart-rate and SpO\u2082 sensor combines the advanced Analog Devices MAX86174A photoplethysmography (PPG) front end with dual Vishay VEMD1060X01 silicon PIN photodiodes and four LEDs (two green, one red, one IR) for multi-wavelength reflective optical sensing.  The 20-bit ADC with a 256-word FIFO provides data at configurable rates from 1 to 2048 frames per second for external processing.",
